{
  "stem": "15768.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And there were no direct connections, so if somebody wanted to call in the middle of the country, we used to have to hopscotch from New York to Ohio to-- to some other stop in order to get to Arizona.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And you had to be pretty fast at it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Otherwise the company docked you for minutes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[DRINKING]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was a very busy person I had no time for extracurricular activities or social-- anything social at all.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was all-- I was hell bent on education, so to speak.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And again, made contracts with the principal.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I needed my languages, and so I told the principal I would take one year of French, attend classes, and then I wanted to take the three-year Regent Exam in French, which of course was bluffing, and the four-year German Regents Exam for college entrance after taking a year of classroom attendance.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it was a furious battle.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My grammar was atrocious.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I wrote magnificent translations and fluent papers where you had to tell stories or relate stories and things.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I remember the principal standing at the door of my German class and fighting with the German teacher.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he said, no, he would not pass her.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My-- my grammar was atrocious, and the principal saying, have you ever in all your teaching career had a translation like this or a paper like this?",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And in the end, the principal won out, and I got my credits for both the French and the German, which was a big help because I didn't have room in my program for this kind of thing.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, there was no fooling around.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I needed every moment, every possible moment.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that's how I battled my way through the American educational system from the word go.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
